title: Kąkolewo, Gmina Grodzisk Wielkopolski
summary:
Kąkolewo [kɔnkɔˈlɛvɔ] (German: Konkolewo) is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Grodzisk Wielkopolski, within Grodzisk Wielkopolski County, Greater Poland Voivodeship, in west-central Poland. It lies approximately 10 kilometres (6 mi) west of Grodzisk Wielkopolski and 51 km (32 mi) west of the regional capital Poznań.
The village has a population of 699.
